OL,3,CGuernsey mums create website to
OL,4,Calleviate cost of living pressures
OL,6,FA pair of working mums from Guernsey
OL,7,Fhave created a price comparison
OL,8,Fwebsite to help families cope with the
OL,9,Fcost of living crisis.
OL,11,FSarah and Kat started
OL,12,F'SuperSavvySavers' to help islanders
OL,13,Fsave money on food and energy bills.
OL,15,FThe website compares supermarket and
OL,16,Fother consumer prices on the island.
