OL,3,CGuernsey mums create website to
OL,4,Calleviate cost of living pressures
OL,6,FWhile recent figures have shown that
OL,7,Finflation is decreasing in Guernsey,
OL,8,Fenergy costs are still soaring, with
OL,9,Fthe rise in 'fuel and light' prices
OL,10,Fincreasing by 12.1% since June last
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,FKat Gillespie says they have been
OL,14,Ffeeling the effects of the rise in
OL,15,Fprices of everyday goods.
OL,17,FShe explained: "We're feeling it and I
OL,18,Fdon't know how single parents are
OL,19,Fsurviving at the moment.
