OL,3,CGuernsey mums create website to
OL,4,Calleviate cost of living pressures
OL,6,F"People are finding it difficult
OL,7,Fbecause everything's gone up; the
OL,8,Fhousehold bills, electricity has gone
OL,9,Fup, insurance has gone sky high,
OL,10,Finterest rates paying the mortgage,
OL,11,Fand that's before you look at the
OL,12,Fweekly shop."
OL,14,FHowever, the pair say that
OL,15,Fsupermarkets have responded to their
OL,16,Fposts and claim that they are working
OL,17,Fto drive prices down.
