OL,3,CGuernsey mums create website to
OL,4,Calleviate cost of living pressures
OL,6,FSarah remains hopeful that prices will
OL,7,Fcome down: "We've been checking the
OL,8,Fprices since back in April for the
OL,9,Fprice comparisons and already there's
OL,10,Fbeen price drops along 25 essential
OL,11,Fitems.
OL,13,F"So fingers crossed we continue to see
OL,14,Fthat happen."
OL,16,FLocal charitable causes say they are
OL,17,Fseeing a higher demand for their
OL,18,Fservices as people look to save money.
