OL,6,FShiloh Church, which runs a food bank
OL,7,Fand provides school uniforms to those
OL,8,Fin need, said they have seen more
OL,9,Fpeople looking for support in the past
OL,10,F12 months.
OL,12,FTeam leader at the church, Chrissie
OL,13,FSalmon, explained: "People have been
OL,14,Fstruggling with interest rates going
OL,15,Fup and life has changed generally for
OL,16,Fpeople (...) the challenge is greater
OL,17,Fthan it's ever been.
